{"id":4340,"date":"2013-08-10T13:05:34","date_gmt":"2013-08-10T12:05:34","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/altlab.org\/?p=4340"},"modified":"2013-08-10T13:05:34","modified_gmt":"2013-08-10T12:05:34","slug":"workshop-home-domotics-with-arduino","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/altlab.org\/2013\/08\/10\/workshop-home-domotics-with-arduino\/","title":{"rendered":"Workshop Home Domotics with Arduino"},"content":{"rendered":"<h3><a href=\"http:\/\/altlab.org\/2013\/08\/10\/workshop-home-domotics-with-arduino\/#WHOMEDOMOTICS\"><strong>Mais informa\u00e7\u00f5es e inscri\u00e7\u00f5es<\/strong><\/a><\/h3>\n<h3><a href=\"http:\/\/altlab.org\/2013\/08\/10\/workshop-home-domotics-with-arduino\/#WHOMEDOMOTICS\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-4258\" title=\"Workshops Controlo de Motores\" alt=\"Workshops Controlo de Motores\" src=\"http:\/\/altlab.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2013\/08\/workshops-altlab-flyer_Domotica.jpg\" width=\"552\" height=\"842\"><\/a><\/h3>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><!--more--><\/p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 18px;\"><a name=\"WHOMEDOMOTICS\"><\/a><\/p>\n<h4 style=\"font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: normal;\">Workshop Home Domotics with Arduino<\/h4>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p class=\"p2\">A Dom\u00f3\u00adti\u00adca \u00e9 um&nbsp;mundo!<br>\nJ\u00e1 todos sonh\u00e1\u00admos, algu\u00adma vez, ter uma casa inte\u00adli\u00adgen\u00adte, com um c\u00e9re\u00adbro esti\u00adlo <span class=\"caps\">HAL9000<\/span>, que conhe\u00adce a nos\u00adsa voz e res\u00adpon\u00adde aos nos\u00adsos comandos!<br>\nTer o dom\u00ed\u00adnio da Ilu\u00admi\u00adna\u00ad\u00e7\u00e3o, Tem\u00adpe\u00adra\u00adtu\u00adra, Mul\u00adti\u00adm\u00e9\u00addia e tudo o mais que pos\u00adsa\u00admos inte\u00adra\u00adgir l\u00e1 em casa, no bot\u00e3o de um tele\u00adco\u00adman\u00addo, num ecr\u00e3 t\u00e1c\u00adtil ou no tele\u00adm\u00f3\u00advel, inclu\u00adsi\u00adv\u00e9 a res\u00adpon\u00adder a coman\u00addos ver\u00adbais, \u00e9 hoje pos\u00ads\u00ed\u00advel gra\u00ad\u00e7as aos avan\u00ad\u00e7os tec\u00adno\u00adl\u00f3\u00adgi\u00adcos em elec\u00adtr\u00f3\u00adni\u00adca e inform\u00e1tica.<br>\nNo entan\u00adto, um sis\u00adte\u00adma de Dom\u00f3\u00adti\u00adca que inclua Cli\u00adma\u00adti\u00adza\u00ad\u00e7\u00e3o, Alar\u00admes, sis\u00adte\u00adma de Rega, inte\u00adrac\u00ad\u00e7\u00e3o com um Tele\u00adfo\u00adne, liga\u00ad\u00e7\u00e3o ao <span class=\"caps\">PC<\/span>, \u00e1 Inter\u00adnet, entre outros, \u00e9 geral\u00admen\u00adte mui\u00adto (mes\u00admo mui\u00adto) oneroso.<br>\nIsso dei\u00adxa de par\u00adte a mai\u00ador par\u00adte dos ama\u00addo\u00adres e hobistas.&nbsp;\ud83d\ude41<br>\nOu&nbsp;n\u00e3o?<br>\nCom a aju\u00adda do Ardui\u00adno, n\u00e3o \u00e9 assim t\u00e3o dif\u00ed\u00adcil mon\u00adtar uma peque\u00adna par\u00adte do con\u00adtro\u00adlo dom\u00e9s\u00adti\u00adco e assim satis\u00adfa\u00adzer o nos\u00adso ego hac\u00adker: Vamos agar\u00adrar um punha\u00addo de sen\u00adso\u00adres e actu\u00ada\u00addo\u00adres Hi-tech mas Low-cost e mon\u00adtar a nos\u00adsa pr\u00f3\u00adpria auto\u00adma\u00ad\u00e7\u00e3o caseira!&nbsp;\ud83d\ude1b<br>\nSe j\u00e1 tens Dom\u00f3\u00adti\u00adca em casa, podes inte\u00adra\u00adgir com o sis\u00adte\u00adma (se f\u00f4r <span class=\"caps\">X10<\/span>) usan\u00addo o Ardui\u00adno e alguns conhe\u00adci\u00admen\u00adtos b\u00e1sicos!<br>\nSe tive\u00adres um pro\u00adt\u00f3\u00adti\u00adpo que quei\u00adras inte\u00adgrar na auto\u00adma\u00ad\u00e7\u00e3o da tua casa, este \u00e9 o momen\u00adto: tr\u00e1-lo e vamos tirar dele o m\u00e1xi\u00admo rendimento!<\/p>\n<p>O altlab for\u00adne\u00adce todos os mate\u00adri\u00adais, s\u00f3 tens que tra\u00adzer o teu lap\u00adtop com o <span class=\"caps\">IDE<\/span> do Ardui\u00adno instalado.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Con\u00adcei\u00adtos abordados:<\/strong><br>\n\u2014 Intro\u00addu\u00ad\u00e7\u00e3o \u00e1 Dom\u00f3tica<br>\n\u2014 O Ardui\u00adno como cen\u00adtral de Dom\u00f3tica<br>\n\u2014 Sen\u00adso\u00adres e actu\u00ada\u00addo\u00adres low-cost<br>\n\u2014 Cabla\u00adgem (qua\u00adli\u00adda\u00adde do sinal e Interfer\u00eacias)<br>\n\u2014 Comu\u00adni\u00adca\u00ad\u00e7\u00f5es sem fio (infra-ver\u00adme\u00adlhos, blu\u00ade\u00adto\u00adoth, r\u00e1dio, ethernet)<br>\n\u2014 Conec\u00adto\u00adres e Adaptadores<br>\n\u2014 Dife\u00adren\u00ad\u00e7as de poten\u00adci\u00adal e iso\u00adla\u00admen\u00adto galv\u00e2nico<br>\n\u2014 Ligar e des\u00adli\u00adgar electrodom\u00e9sticos<br>\n\u2014 Coman\u00addos direc\u00adtos e Macros (Ambi\u00aden\u00adtes)<br>\n\u2014 Sis\u00adte\u00admas Pas\u00adsi\u00advos (ape\u00adnas res\u00adpon\u00addem a coman\u00addos directos)<br>\n\u2014 Sis\u00adte\u00admas Inte\u00adli\u00adgen\u00adtes (exis\u00adte um algo\u00adrit\u00admo que emi\u00adte comandos)<br>\n\u2014 Espan\u00ads\u00e3o do Sistema<br>\n\u2014 Uni\u00adda\u00adde de Ali\u00admen\u00adta\u00ad\u00e7\u00e3o Inin\u00adter\u00adrup\u00adta (ges\u00adt\u00e3o e comu\u00adni\u00adca\u00ad\u00e7\u00e3o com a&nbsp;<span class=\"caps\">UPS<\/span>)<br>\n\u2014 Seguran\u00e7a<br>\n\u2014 Redund\u00e2ncia<br>\n\u2014 Comu\u00adni\u00adca\u00ad\u00e7\u00f5es com <span class=\"caps\">PC<\/span> e outros microcontroladores<br>\n\u2014 <span class=\"caps\">X10<\/span> e a bibli\u00ado\u00adte\u00adca do Ardui\u00adno para Dom\u00f3tica<\/p>\n<p><strong>Pr\u00e1\u00adti\u00adcas:<\/strong><br>\n\u2014 Usan\u00addo Sen\u00adso\u00adres em casa (Ilu\u00admi\u00adna\u00ad\u00e7\u00e3o, Tem\u00adpe\u00adra\u00adtu\u00adra, Intru\u00ads\u00e3o, outros)<br>\n\u2014 Usar c\u00e2ma\u00adras de v\u00eddeo (web\u00adcam e ipcam) para acti\u00advar alar\u00admes e\/ ou envi\u00adar imagens<br>\n\u2014 Apli\u00adcan\u00addo Actu\u00ada\u00addo\u00adres para simu\u00adlar pre\u00adsen\u00ad\u00e7a (mexer cor\u00adti\u00adnas, pro\u00advo\u00adcar som\u00adbras e\/ ou&nbsp;sons)<br>\n\u2014 Actu\u00adar dis\u00adpo\u00adsi\u00adti\u00advos de alar\u00adme como Sire\u00adnes ou cha\u00adma\u00adda tele\u00adf\u00f3\u00adni\u00adca ou de&nbsp;v\u00eddeo.<\/p>\n<p>Este work\u00adshop ser\u00e1 ori\u00aden\u00adtado <span class=\"GRspelling\">por<\/span> Rui Mar\u00adce\u00adli\u00adno (Mem\u00adbro altLab).<\/p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 13px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 18px;\"><strong>Ins\u00adcri\u00ad\u00e7\u00f5es<\/strong> : <a href=\"http:\/\/altlab.org\/event-registration\/#WHOMEDOMOTICS\" target=\"_blank\"><b><span class=\"caps\">AQUI<\/span><\/b> (a ins\u00adcri\u00ad\u00e7\u00e3o on-line \u00e9 obrigat\u00f3ria)<\/a><br>\n<strong>Pre\u00ad\u00e7o<\/strong> : 30\u20ac. Mem\u00adbros do altLab s\u00f3 pagam 20\u20ac ;p<br>\n<strong>Local<\/strong> : no altLab, \u00e9 cla\u00adro! (<a href=\"http:\/\/maps.google.com\/maps\/ms?daddr=&amp;saddr=Praceta+Domingos+Rodrigues,+Loures+2685,+Portugal&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hl=en&amp;doflg=ptk&amp;msa=0&amp;ll=38.784465,-9.127729&amp;spn=0.004382,0.010568&amp;t=h&amp;z=17&amp;msid=207816408522249587914.00049d2e29ed5bcfba45e\" target=\"_blank\">Pra\u00adce\u00adta Domin\u00adgos Rodri\u00adgues, n\u00ba2<\/a>)<\/p>\n<p>C\u00e1 te esperamos!<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Mais infor\u00adma\u00ad\u00e7\u00f5es e inscri\u00e7\u00f5es&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":11,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"wp_typography_post_enhancements_disabled":false},"categories":[8],"tags":[50,121],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/altlab.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4340"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/altlab.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/altlab.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/altlab.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/11"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/altlab.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4340"}],"version-history":[{